extensionMeta.name: Sheet Navigation & Actions
extensionMeta.description: Sense Sheet Navigation + Actions visualization extension for Qlik Sense.
extensionMeta.author: Stefan Walther

bundle.name: Dashboard bundle
bundle.description:
This is a set of extensions that will facilitate dashboard creation in Qlik Sense: A navigation button, a date picker, a slider, and two different container objects. These can be used in addition to the native objects found under "Charts".

For limitations and support conditions, see the documentation.

qStringExpression.qExpr:
=num(Count({<IsOccupiedFlg={'0'}, IsOfflineFlg={'0'}, FactType={'10'}>+<IsSemiPrivateResidentFlg={'1'}, IsOfflineFlg={'0'}, SemiRate={">0"}, FactType={'10'}>}[IsOccupiedFlg]),'#,##0.;(#,##0.)')
&' Available Rooms -- '&num(sum({<IsOccupiedFlg={0}, IsOfflineFlg={'0'}, MonthYear=, Status=>}SpecialRate)
+
sum({<IsSemiPrivateResidentFlg={'1'}, IsOfflineFlg={'0'}, SemiRate={">0"}, MonthYear=, Status=>}SemiRate),'$#,##0.;($#,##0.)')&' Revenue Potential'
'Available Rooms = Occupancy Report Vacant Rooms - Offline Rooms + Half Occupied Semi Private'

qProperty.footnote: Half-Occupied Semi-Privates to sell does not take into consideration license capacity.
